<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Dec 2021 07:57:56 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Sony 展示 AI 機械手，自調力度夾起鮮花不會爛</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/10/sony-shows-off-a-robot-grabber-4k-oled-panels-for-vr-and-more/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-shows-off-a-robot-grabber-4k-oled-panels-for-vr-and-more</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 10 Dec 2021 07:57:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[OLED 微型顯示器]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><category><![CDATA[低延遲頭戴裝置系統]]></category><category><![CDATA[機械手]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1075192</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Sony 日前舉辦 Sony Technology Day，公開旗下集團研發中心與各事業部門的研發成果。當中較 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 日前舉辦 Sony Technology Day，公開旗下集團研發中心與各事業部門的研發成果。當中較為矚目的，莫過於採用 OLED 微型顯示器與低延遲技術的 VR 虛擬實境頭戴裝置的研發原型，以及可自動調節握持力度的機械手。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">OLED 微型顯示器及低延遲頭戴裝置系統的研發原型，採用了單眼 4K、合計 8K 的一吋等級 OLED 微型顯示器。透過在影像感測器開發製造的加工製程技術，加上顯示器研發的裝置與電路技術，在手機螢幕約 20 分之 1 的尺寸中整合超過 2 倍的像素，消除過往採用透鏡放大畫面的像素感，提升視覺效果；裝置中更加入延遲補償技術，利用多組感測器，即時追蹤觀看者頭部位置，在 0.01 秒的時間內修正畫面後再行顯示，以消除顯示延遲、減少使用 VR 時的暈眩感。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075194" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C927ABE6-8D85-4C6C-B0D6-BFCA2FE92AFD.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-694x382.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-694x382.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-1280x704.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-768x422.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-1536x845.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796-2048x1126.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/9C7EC5F6-A3B7-4877-B266-63ED6B44B796.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075196" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-694x382.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-694x382.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-1280x705.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-768x423.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-1536x846.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD-2048x1128.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6B95ED9E-9633-4490-A1F8-9B0A38CE75FD.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_53030"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xHuqsHmHkZM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">此外，Sony 今次亦展示了可透過 AI 自動調節握持力度的機械手，它可以因應手持不同的物件調節力度，甚至中途改變力度防止物件掉下。在 Sony 的官方影片中可見，Sony 機械手在接過玫瑰花時，即使握著花朵部分，也不會令花朵損壞；機械手亦可以作出兩手配合的動作，一隻機械手握著杯子，另一隻機械手握著樽子，然後做出倒水動作。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1075197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/6439CC5A-815B-4AF8-8E05-4C0E60579258.gif" alt="" width="640" height="360" /></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_22317"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T6vX7FcBQMs?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2021/12/8/22823188/sony-technology-day-presentation-vr-oled-screens-robot-grabber">THE VERGE</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
